{"tid":2002576,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"再有中概股回歸　傳網易已申請來港第二上市","createTime":"2020-05-05T09:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T11:34:21.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04ec7a035c7f07da100a774d9e045bf6d9bb45ce","tid":2002576,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2630000/2634676/050520_NET_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2630000%2F2634676%2F050520_NET_1024.jpg&h=fdb168ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在美上市的網易（NTES）傳已向港交所（00388）遞交在香港第二上市申請，網易為中國第二大手機遊戲商，排名僅次騰訊（00700）。現時網易市值約430億美元，暫時未有發行規模和上市時間等細節。而據消息指，集團最早可能在下半年於港交所掛牌。有理由相信，網易會是繼阿里巴巴（09988）後，另一次矚目的中概股回歸。<br />\n<br />\n據美國20-F文件顯示，截至去年底，網易CEO丁磊持有14.56億股或45.1%股權，Orbis Investment為第二大股東，持股6.5%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而網易回歸，或繼續引起中概股回歸潮，最大贏家相信就是港交所。港交所上月指出，2018年及2019年分別有32間及47間新經濟公司來港掛牌，又指出自新規實施後，在港上市的新經濟公司市值，佔本港股市總市值的17%。從2017年起上市的新經濟公司，佔港股日均成交的比率，由2017年的4.1%增至15.4%。<span style=\"color: red;\">而包括阿里、網易，以及市傳會回歸的京東（JD）在內，全是新經濟公司</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回家了,大伙們都回家了,港交所永遠歡迎你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a9ddf6bb1930fca3be67e1813bf6a158c6023b","tid":2002576,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />凱旋歸來"},{"pid":"c65e20a5d6513c80fcea859c9944d2f89ed9a9ba","tid":2002576,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br